org.apache.commons.math4.stat.descriptive

Class AbstractUnivariateStatistic

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.math4.stat.descriptive.AbstractUnivariateStatistic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UnivariateStatistic, MathArrays.Function
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Percentile, SemiVariance

    public abstract class AbstractUnivariateStatistic
extends java.lang.Object
implements UnivariateStatistic
    Abstract base class for implementations of the UnivariateStatistic interface.

    Provides a default implementation of evaluate(double[]), delegating to evaluate(double[], int, int) in the natural way.
